\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />more la <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab5ba157f572c557292f0f9622ba373d20701b01","tid":2395310,"uid":48234,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"2eac1f41428a11dd58b676fb96389d073fcec370","tid":2395310,"uid":327593,"like":14,"dislike":134,"score":-120,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T21:54:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T11:50:30.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">連登日報&mdash;支持獨裁政權者，無權享有言論自由<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1180589\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1180589</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/emWjmNa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FemWjmNa.jpg&h=c08f65f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n請問numnumchu(狗隻#327593)你屙尿嗰陣起左腳定右腳?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2396219\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2396219</a></span></span>"},{"pid":"2d3844cce2b48068e3e3fed44ef7029bb70934c1","tid":2395310,"uid":662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T11:51:31.000Z","msg":"加油呀！唔好放棄！"},{"pid":"92846e2bfa2338fdf1f40bcc22b0aca275cfb20f","tid":2395310,"uid":198769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T12:36:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0999f2aeb973fd9f5423441fb8aa33954f04e622","tid":2395310,"uid":129676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T12:40:04.000Z","msg":"同巴打經歷差唔多<br />\n不過加埋今鋪已經數唔清第幾次低潮<br />\n就快挨唔到落去"},{"pid":"fa1234f6d38b7eb917f9aaaf389ebac1ea58d28f","tid":2395310,"uid":121548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T12:42:14.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"f46f81f76b673079e7640d3acff15e67e7dcca18","tid":2395310,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T12:45:26.000Z","msg":"頂住<br />\n未來未必更好<br />\n不過人生就係咁"},{"pid":"32fbd018e63730e6cc42f659c8a73d8d880563f0","tid":2395310,"uid":122513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5341bdde8f7be6bb6bbf919a9d4ab4788dc33ff0","tid":2395310,"uid":286473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T21:50:39.000Z","msg":"比起錢，你經歷既好少事<br />\n見到兩個case都輸10萬8萬而自殺<br />\n真係唔值，幾年前我都試過大喜大跌好多<br />\n覺得對屋企人唔住，就乖乖地返份工每個月比多幾千蚊家用<br />\n<br />\n我係自殺過來人<br />\n兩個月來我試過三次<br />\n入過院，依家條頸仲有條疤痕<br />\n我連聽日有無錢食飯都唔知<br />\n由12起到上星期<br />\n女友背叛<br />\n講出嚟嘅藉口最大嘅分歧因為政見<br />\n1個好友，1個親人過身<br />\n失業，我而家有案底搵工都好困難<br />\n全部野一次過發生 <br />\n我去到而家都好想再了結一次自己<br />\n至少你哋都仲有份工，仲有書讀下<br />\n呢段時間我完全冇動力繼續生存<br />\n你試下努力先，我無動力，比我行先<br />\n<br />\n如果你淨係覺得因為GME而去死<br />\n真心講句唔撚值，唔係想同佢地鬥慘<br />\n但如果要講係咪應該了結自己<br />\n我相信我比你地更加應該了結自己先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T16:30:46.000Z","msg":"或許我不能完全了解你內心的痛苦，但我也曾置身於無助和絕望之中，明白身處痛苦是怎樣一回事。無論你的是否想放棄自己，也希望你不要將困擾藏在心裡，因鬱結和壓力積存得太多太久，到情緒爆發時可能已超出你所能控制的程度。<br />\n<br />\n你不如停一停，到我們的網站  <a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk&d=GtJgxCFvwMhqeg%2B2Fxb9EaC2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=d00e5c0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>  。 那裡有一些勵志故事、有趣短片，也有與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看。您更可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：下午4時至凌晨1時；星期六、日及公眾假期：晚上８時至凌晨１時），即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"b0ef96dbdabe70c34a02702d82cc902118dfdebe","tid":2395310,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab1a5b1ec9bfb5da39c5c484134c69f0548d1cd4","tid":2395310,"uid":49204,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T03:32:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nd90Fi3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNd90Fi3.png&h=a587fd70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n收檔啦屌你老母<br />\n又想出黎博咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上年貼左條payme link出黎食人血饅頭仲未夠飽？<br />\n定係又賭錢賭大左要出黎叫救命呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T02:10:05.000Z","msg":"等陣先，呢個邊個嚟?"}]}